"   (For additional information",
"   <a class=\"drug drug_patient\" href=\"mobipreview.htm?14/61/15317?source=see_link\">",
"    see \"Amitriptyline and chlordiazepoxide: Patient drug information\"",
"   </a>",
"   )",
"   <br/>",
"   For abbreviations and symbols that may be used in Lexicomp (",
